quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  56,70,"Tí A bá fẹ́ ni, Àwa ìbá ṣe é ní omi tó móró. Ẹ ò ṣe máa dúpẹ́?"
  56,71,"Ẹ sọ fún Mi nípa iná tí ẹ̀ ń dá,"
  56,72,"ṣé ẹ̀yin l’ẹ ṣẹ̀dá igi rẹ̀ ni tàbí Àwa ni Aṣẹ̀dá?"
  67,10,"Wọ́n tún wí pé: “Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé a gbọ́ràn ni tàbí pé a ṣe làákàyè ni, àwa kò níí wà nínú èrò inú Iná tó ń jó.”"
  67,11,"Wọ́n sì jẹ́wọ́ ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ wọn. Nítorí náà, ìjìnnà sí ìkẹ́ Allāhu yó wà fún àwọn èrò inú Iná tó ń jó."
  67,12,"Dájúdájú àwọn tó ń páyà Olúwa wọn ní ìkọ̀kọ̀, àforíjìn àti ẹ̀san tó tóbi ń bẹ fún wọn."
  68,4,"Dájúdájú ìwọ sì wà lórí ìwà ńlá (ìwà alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé)."
  68,5,"Láìpẹ́ ìwọ yóò rí i, àwọn náà yó sì rí i;"
  68,6,"èwo nínú yín ni aládàn-ánwò (wèrè)?"
  69,1,"Ìṣẹ̀lẹ̀ Òdodo náà!"
  69,2,"Kí ni Ìṣẹ̀lẹ̀ Òdodo náà?"
  69,3,"Kí sì ni ó mú ọ mọ ohun tó ń jẹ́ Ìṣẹ̀lẹ̀ Òdodo náà?"